Sri Lanka Inflation ‘Under Control,’ Fitch Rating’s Woo Says

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-07-19T06:56:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/sri-lanka-inflation-under-control-fitch-rating-s-woo-says.html
Sri Lanka ’s inflation is “under
control” and Fitch Ratings is comfortable with the island’s
monetary policy stance, Art Woo, director Asia-Pacific
Sovereign, said in a conference call today.  Fitch upgraded Sri Lanka’s long-term foreign and local
currency issuer default ratings by a notch to BB- from B+. The
outlooks on both ratings are stable, Fitch said in a statement
yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
